title: Easy up Team collaboration using Icebreaker Bot
sortTitle: easy up team collaboration using icebreaker bot
description: The session will give attendees the grips into why Microsoft teams has become the center focus on enhancing collaboration, it is now very important to lay a solid foundation to enhance the selection process in building suitable team member bonds, Team culture is the glue that holds an organization together.In this session we will be looking for an artificial intelligence bot, that is benefiting from in shaping our team culture in any organization especially using Microsoft teams.We also look at some other enabler that has been injected to make collaboration easy and more focus in a digital world.
